title: TrueUSD pauses minting of TUSD via Prime Trust, stablecoin briefly depegs
description: In a June 10 post on its verified Twitter account, TrueUSD informed its users that the minting of TUSD tokens via Prime Trust has been temporarily paused until further notice

title: Cardano developer, IOG, insists ADA is not a security, token down 36% in 5 days
description: ADA, the native currency of Cardano, a blockchain smart contracts platform and Ethereum competitor, is not a security, the lead developer of the network, Input Output Global (IOG) insists
